snippet.title: Steam Trailer - Meta Revelations - Armour of the Abyss
snippet.description:
Adapt your armour and save the world!

Wishlist now! https://store.steampowered.com/app/2749360/META_REVELATIONS__ARMOUR_OF_THE_ABYSS/

A turn based RPG where you can adapt your armour and save the world! You are Adena Krieger - a cold blooded huntress. Uncover your mysterious past and prevent a calamity that is written in your name.

Coming Soon.
